## Development

This project uses [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) for dependency management
and a `make`-based quality pipeline.

```bash
make check      # full quality pipeline (format, lint, type, security, test)
make ci         # same pipeline, no auto-format (for CI)
make test       # tests only
make build      # build wheel and sdist into work/dist/
make publish    # publish to PyPI (requires credentials)
```

## Quality standards

- **Formatting** — ruff format
- **Linting** — ruff + flake8 (complexity ≤ 10)
- **Type checking** — mypy (strict)
- **Security** — bandit + pip-audit
- **Tests** — pytest with 100 % coverage requirement
